title: Call The Priest, Alia Bhatt Has A Confession To Make!
text:
Natasha Patel Mar . 17 . 2017 Alia Bhatt 
Alright, so maybe the Priest wont be tooo concerned about Alia Bhatt ‘s confession, but we sure are! In fact we’re in LOVE with her latest airport outfit. Wearing a sweatshirt with a printed slogan that reads “#LURKER”, we’re literally just dying—because how true is that? While Alia might have just told the world her stalker habits, we still think her outfit is fashion and airport-worthy! Alia Bhatt 
Also, it’s a blush pink! I mean, it’s practically a 10 on 10 for me with this outfit. 
Taking it a notch higher, her OOTN from last night was quite sexy… Alia Bhatt 
Guess we’re all #LURKERS ;) 0
